  </d4p_eqn_inline>
</b>
. This will be the length of the projection of 
<d4p_eqn_inline>
  <mathml><m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mover accent="true"><m:mrow><m:mi>P</m:mi><m:mo>'</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>P</m:mi><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="true">⟶</m:mo></m:mover></m:mrow></m:math></mathml>
